int CALICE::DecoderSet::getModuleID ( const unsigned int  module,
const unsigned int  chip,
const unsigned int  channel 
) const [inline, inherited]

get (Module) channel ID from triple module, chip, channel

The right encoding string has to be set before.

Warning:
This (Module) channel ID will only contain information about module, chip and channel. If the encoding string contains additional fields this will have value 0.
See also:
setModuleEncoding
